                "type": "element",
                "tag": "em",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "In the world of Krynn, many refer to the Mages of High Sorcery as the Wizards of High Sorcery. The organization accepts more than wizards, though, with sorcerers, warlocks, and other spellcasters included among their ranks."
